title: Elie Saab goes green for pret-a-porter collection
description:
(30 Sep 2017) ELIE SAAB GOES GREEN FOR PRET-A-PORTER COLLECTION
The Grand Palais turned into a human jungle at Elie Saab Spring Summer 2018 show, in Paris, Saturday (30 SEPT. 2017)
The Amazon forest was celebrated in every outfit in the collection by the Lebanese designer.
Different shades of green were displayed in the maxi long dresses, with high-cut fringes evocating leafs, serpent prints, silky jackets and other bright colors such as warm yellow, hibiscus red or waterfall blue. The whole ensemble gave the impression of a living jungle. 
As usual, several famous models walked the runway for Eliee Saab: Dominican Lineisy Montero, Portuguese Sara Sampaio,French Cindy Bruna, American Martha Hunt, Canadian Winnie Harlow and New Zealand Georgia Fowler. Also present sitting front row was American socialite Olivia Palermo, and Princess of Thailand Sirivannavari Nariratana.
